<BaseLayout title="About Tobias Treppmann" description="Learn about Tobias Treppmann, founder of Oratio&Co">


  <!-- Main Content -->
  <article style="max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 4rem 2rem;">
    <h1>About Tobias Treppmann</h1>

    <p>Tobias Treppmann is a product designer, theologian, and mentor helping churches and Christian organizations navigate change through strategic design and theological reflection.</p>

    <h2>What He Does</h2>
    <p>Tobias combines deep expertise in product design and human-centered innovation with a genuine passion for the global church. He believes that good design and theological depth don't have to be in tension—in fact, they strengthen each other.</p>

    <p>His work focuses on:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Strategic Ministry Consulting</strong> — helping church leaders clarify their mission and operationalize their vision</li>
      <li><strong>Design Thinking for Ministry</strong> — applying human-centered design principles to ministry challenges</li>
      <li><strong>Digital Spiritual Formation</strong> — building products and platforms that foster genuine spiritual growth in community</li>
      <li><strong>Missional Innovation</strong> — equipping churches to contextualize the gospel and thrive in rapidly changing contexts</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Current Work</h2>
    <p><strong>BibelTV:</strong> As a product designer, Tobias helps shape digital resources for Christian education and spiritual formation.</p>

    <p><strong>Aperto:</strong> Founder and lead designer of Aperto (aperto.bible), a digital spiritual formation platform designed for meaningful Scripture engagement in community.</p>

    <p><strong>Kairos University:</strong> Pursuing a Master of Arts in Missional Leadership, exploring the intersection of theology, culture, and organizational change.</p>

    <p><strong>Oratio&Co:</strong> Founder and principal consultant, working with churches and ministry organizations on strategic design, theological reflection, and innovation.</p>

    <h2>Speaking & Teaching</h2>
    <p>Tobias is an invited speaker and workshop facilitator. Recent speaking includes:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>ICCM Europe 2023: "Navigating Fluid Contexts" and "Missional Design — Lean Startup for Churches"</li>
      <li>Various church leadership conferences and ministry networks across Europe</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Get in Touch</h2>
    <p>Interested in exploring strategic design, missional innovation, or digital spiritual formation for your church or organization?</p>
    <p style="margin-top: 1.5rem;">
      <strong style="color: var(--color-dark);">Email:</strong> <EmailLink /><br/>
      <strong style="color: var(--color-dark);">Explore:</strong> <a href="https://missional.design" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">missional.design</a> | <a href="https://aperto.bible" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">aperto.bible</a>
    </p>
  </article>


</BaseLayout>

